API.ADK

Enum ReturnCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ReturnCode>
      • API.ADK.ReturnCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ReturnCode>

    public enum ReturnCode
extends java.lang.Enum<ReturnCode>
    Enum of all return codes. These return codes are used in almost all methods and also used as error messages.
    Author:
    hroesdiyono
